title: PE bags on roll making machine US-JDAP-400*2
title_uz: Polietilen rulonli paket ishlab chiqarish uskunasi US-JDAP-400*2
title_ru: Оборудование для производства полиэтиленовых рулонных пакетов US-JDAP-400*2
title_en: PE bags on roll making machine US-JDAP-400*2
short_description: These types of bags, which are mainly used in shopping malls and stores, have become an integral part of our lives. This US-JDAP-400*2 model equipment consists of a 2-line working area and is capable of producing 60 to 350 bags per minute per line. The total power of the equipment is 19.5 kW, its weight is 2800 kg, and its dimensions are 6200*2200*1900 mm. Other models are also shown in the description. They differ in price and parameters.
short_description_uz: Asosan savdo markazlari va do'konlarda ishlatiladigan bu turdagi paketlar hayotimizning ajralmas qismiga aylanib ulgurdi. Bu US-JDAP-400*2 modeldagi uskuna 2 qatorli ish hududidan tarkib topgan va har bir qator daqiqasiga 60 tadan 350 tagacha paket ishlab chiqarish imkoniyatiga ega. Uskunaning umumiy quvvati 19.5 kW, vazni 2800 kg, o'lchamlari esa 6200*2200*1900 mm. Tavsifda boshqa modellar ham aks etgan. Ular narx va parametrlarda bir-biridan farqlanadi.

Общая мощность оборудования 19,5 кВт, вес 2800 кг, размеры 6200*2200*1900 мм. Другие модели также указаны в описании. Они различаются по цене и параметрам.
